text.tspan: the loop(s) in the tree strap
Tree straps protect the trees! Please use them.
Wrap each tree with a tree strap to protect the bark
Attach the first rope to the tree
Pull the hammock out of the bag and attach the second rope
Hang the hammock so that the ridgeline is just taught
It will take a little practice to get used to centering the hammock
